{"tid":1650082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人] 係咩叫你堅持落去 一人放底一個原因","createTime":"2019-10-12T20:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T17:27:52.000Z","uid":244058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d935f830218195821445558c0531dbdb8ca52c51","tid":1650082,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:22:24.000Z","msg":"係咩叫你堅持到宜家？ <br />\n我係希望見到所有犯法既黑警坐監<br />\n所有\b死者沉冤得雪 <br />\n最重要五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n<br />\n記唔記得612第一粒催淚彈 <br />\n六月個陣 一粒都厭多<br />\n仲有好多手足失蹤 唔知又被棄屍係邊度 <br />\n晚晚都好似宵禁 大家覺唔覺無左好多自由？<br />\n我今日病左帶個口罩出街 <br />\n都要擔心下會唔會俾黑警圍住打我再check身份證 <br />\n香港唔應該係禁架！！ <br />\n但我都堅信有出路 <br />\n10月13見<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojRQzmr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojRQzmr.png&h=0d841859&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f7cdd64155c46514c8da4c6332e8f9fdeb0b4fb","tid":1650082,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UhvazoW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUhvazoW.jpg&h=c599d40c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span>[/red"},{"pid":"51ef3ffcd0173e6127da3c28ad61f03df0d17740","tid":1650082,"uid":246768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:29:30.000Z","msg":"如果我哋放棄<br />\n死去嘅手足喺唔會原諒我哋"},{"pid":"8ccc46542d2682cb8b8c28c0e3537999a9d9024b","tid":1650082,"uid":72801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:31:43.000Z","msg":"未見到光復之後嘅香港<br />\n未參加煲底之約"},{"pid":"df982c072c5c35a32a1681eca0e27e0f8f386dc8","tid":1650082,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:31:50.000Z","msg":"輸咗會入集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ec2ff33e27f11808e6096094b23c30f5a82938","tid":1650082,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ccc46542d2682c